transcript:

Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan ji.
Customer: Haan ji Gupta ji baat kar rahe ho na aap?

Customer: Sir main Nidhi baat kar rahi hu IndiaMART se senior manager kaise hain aap sir?

Executive: Haan ji madam bas main meeting mein hu free hoke aapko call back kar paunga.
Executive: Sure sir koi problem nahi hai. Thank you sir.
Executive: Theek hai ji.
